      <para>
Specifies the connection to the X server.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <emphasis remap='I'>event_mask</emphasis>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
Specifies which pointer events are reported to the client.
